						<summary>

						<p>Vijayanagara, Mallikārjunarāya, Śaka 1380 = A.D. 1458.</p>						

						<p>This records a gift of land for offerings by Tirumēṉi-Aḻagaṉ <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Vīra-Pāṇḍya Vijaiyālaiyadēva. It seems that the nāḍu undertook to pay themselves the taxes on that land.</p>						

						</summary>
